Feat
 Village Takeover - Defuse Scenario

Counter-Terrorists: 
Hold the power substation or the mission
from destruction, or eliminate all 
opposing forces.

Terrorists: 
Make haste towards the power station (A) or
the spanish mission (B) and destroy 
objectives. Alternatively eliminate all 
opposing players.
 
Notes: 
-There are 2 objective sites in this level
-Built for 40 players
